data.clean_description: 5 fresh peyote seeds to start your garden with. The seeds are very small , simply lay them on cactus soil or sand , cover with a seeds thickness of soil , water and watch them grow. Peyote is a small , spineless cactus , Lophophora williams ii , with the hallucinogen mescaline 3 , 4 , 5 - trimethoxyphenethylamine being the principal active ingredient. From earliest recorded time , peyote has been used by natives in northern Mexico and the south - western United States as a part of their religious rites. Order 3 packs and get an extra free. 20 seeds for the price of 15. USA buyers with at least 3 completed orders may stay in escrow until the order arrives. Only 5 for first class postage.
